                                                    </ul>
                                                    <p>When determining what to include in an analytics dashboard, an organization will discover several key performance indicators (KPI) that exist within their data. A key performance indicator (KPI) is a quantitative figure that shows how effective a certain activity has been, whether a department has met its objectives, or whether the firm as a whole is fulfilling expectations. You will be able to see the broad picture much more clearly if you prioritize the data that is most relevant to your organization and include it in your dashboard.<br><br>Website performance is a common example of an operational dashboard that management and executives may utilize in marketing. A website performance dashboard may feature data such as daily or real-time website traffic, bounce rates, a top-performing landing page, new versus returning customers, customer conversion rates, daily revenue earned, top-performing channels, and so on. Monitoring these measures regularly and frequently allows for immediate intervention if any of the main areas are found to be failing.&nbsp;<br><br>Analytical dashboards are the most prevalent type of dashboard seen in business intelligence applications. Analysts use them to study massive data sets to detect trends, anticipate events, and assist organizations in making better decisions.<br><br>Analysts utilizing this type of dashboard may leverage past data from an organization to influence future decisions, such as guiding the growth in ad expenditure during periods when revenue has traditionally increased owing to seasonality.&nbsp;<br>These variables might be seen on a month-to-month line graph across a year, for example, and could also be used to visualize the previous year for a better understanding of growth.<br><br>Analytics dashboards are one of the most powerful resources an organization can invest in if it lacks the expertise, time, or people to manually produce, analyze, and distribute data