                                                <div class="col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12 col-xl-12 pt-10">
                                                    <p>BPM is not a software application. BPM tools can help with the establishment of standard and automated business processes.<br><br>BPM is not synonymous with task management. The administration or organization of a succession of activities is referred to as task or project management. Task and ad hoc project administration can be aided by project management software such as Microsoft Project, Jira, Asana, or Trello. Business Process Management, on the other hand, is concerned largely with recurrent and continuous procedures that follow a predictable pattern or process management.<br><br>Business process management (BPM) is a systematic method for improving company operations. When it is properly implemented, everyone knows how they can help the organization accomplish its goals.<br><br>Synergy provides fully customized easily deployed Business process management systems that lead to a happier, more productive team, which leads to happier customers, more revenues, and fewer expenses.<br></p>
